FileHandling : it is something in which we use to read or write files


IO : input and output

OutputStream : write something in the file
InputStream : what we read something from the file


Student Class
rno, name, std


During writing , object is converted into stream

Stream  is an object, which is in the form of binary text


Serialisation : converting a class object into stream(write)
Deserialisation : converting stream to object.(read)




